What's new in this update:

• The model picker now refreshes when you reconnect, plus a manual refresh button — new AI models show up without restarting the app.
• You'll get a heads-up when your PC's Uxnan bridge needs updating.
• Redesigned Settings, grouped into clear sections, with a new About screen and open-source licenses.
• Improved updates: see download progress and install right from the app, and choose how often to check.

Thanks for testing this alpha!
